OL,3,CEnfield drill rappers found guilty of
OL,4,Cmurder provoked by social media fight
OL,6,FTwo drill rappers have been found
OL,7,Fguilty of murdering an 18-year-old
OL,8,Fman, who was shot dead after an online
OL,9,Fdispute between Enfield gangs.
OL,11,FKenu Harker was shot in the head and
OL,12,Fchest with a pistol in June last year.
OL,14,FEmmanuel Popoola shot him from the
OL,15,Fback of an electric dirt bike, which
OL,16,Fwas ridden by Teyvon Etefia.
OL,18,FThe two 18 year olds were found guilty
OL,19,Fof murder and possessing a self-
OL,20,Floading pistol with intent to endanger
OL,21,Flife at the Old Bailey on Monday.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/10
