CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1783700376
OL,3,CEnfield drill rappers found guilty of
OL,4,Cmurder provoked by social media fight
OL,6,FThe killing came after a series of
OL,7,Fviolent incidents arising from rivalry
OL,8,Fbetween the two gangs.
OL,10,FThe Old Bailey heard that it was
OL,11,Fmotivated by a row on Snapchat.
OL,13,FVoice messages were sent implying that
OL,14,FPopoola could not afford data for his
OL,15,Fmobile phone.
OL,17,FAfterwards, gang members bragged about
OL,18,Fthe murder in drill rap videos.
OL,19,FPopoola performed under the drill rap
OL,20,Fname 'Constancy' jurors were told.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
