CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1783700376
OL,3,CEnfield drill rappers found guilty of
OL,4,Cmurder provoked by social media fight
OL,6,FProsecutor Louise Oakley KC said:
OL,8,F"The speed of the Sur-Ron bike that
OL,9,FEmmanuel Popoola and Tayvon Etefia
OL,10,Fwere on meant they gained ground on
OL,11,FKeanu Harker very quickly and, as they
OL,12,Frode alongside him, Emmanuel Popoola
OL,13,Fshot him.
OL,15,F"He fired three shots from a very
OL,16,Fshort distance. Two of them struck
OL,17,FKeanu Harker in the head and chest.
OL,18,FTayvon Etefia did not flinch.
OL,26,@pD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1783700376
OL,3,CEnfield drill rappers found guilty of
OL,4,Cmurder provoked by social media fight
OL,6,F"Keanu Harker immediately fell off his
OL,7,Fbicycle on to the road. He was fatally
OL,8,Finjured but somehow managed to crawl a
OL,9,Fshort distance into the front garden
OL,10,Fof a residential address just off the
OL,11,FGreat Cambridge Road.
OL,13,F"Emmanuel Popoola and Tayvon did not
OL,14,Fstop. They continued to make good
OL,15,Ftheir escape."
OL,17,FAlerted by the gunshots, witnesses
OL,18,Ffound Mr Harker's bicycle lying in the
OL,19,Froad covered in blood and followed a
OL,20,Ftrail to the victim, who died at the
OL,21,Fscene.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUwD@NO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1783700376
OL,3,CEnfield drill rappers found guilty of
OL,4,Cmurder provoked by social media fight
OL,6,FFollowing the shooting, the defendants
OL,7,Ffled the scene, dumped the e-bike and
OL,8,Fdiscarded their clothes.
OL,10,FEtefia discarded a machete in a
OL,11,Fneighbouring garden.
OL,13,FWithin days after the shooting,
OL,14,FPopoola boarded a one-way Eurostar
OL,15,Fservice from London St Pancras to
OL,16,FParis with the help of his girlfriend.
OL,18,FEtefia booked his own ticket but was
OL,19,Ftracked by police, who boarded the
OL,20,Ftrain and arrested him two minutes
OL,21,Fbefore it due to depart.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1783700376
OL,3,CEnfield drill rappers found guilty of
OL,4,Cmurder provoked by social media fight
OL,6,FPopoola was arrested in his apartment
OL,7,Fby Paris gendarmes.
OL,9,FHe was extradited from France to
OL,10,FLondon and King was arrested on
OL,11,Fsuspicion of assisting an offender.
OL,13,FGiving evidence, Popoola denied being
OL,14,Finvolved in the shooting but was
OL,15,Fimplicated by Etefia, who told jurors
OL,16,Fhe had been on the back of his e-bike
OL,17,Fthat day but he did not know he had a
OL,18,Fgun.
OL,20,FFollowing the verdicts, Mr Harker's
OL,21,Ffamily said:
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1783700376
OL,3,CEnfield drill rappers found guilty of
OL,4,Cmurder provoked by social media fight
OL,6,F"Our son had just turned 18 when these
OL,7,Findividuals decided to take his life.
OL,9,F"We are grateful that some measure of
OL,10,Fjustice has been served, but no amount
OL,11,Fof time they spend in prison will ever
OL,12,Fbe enough for us.
OL,14,F"We have been left with a lifetime of
OL,15,Fpain and loss that can never be undone.
OL,17,F"We hope this case opens people's eyes
OL,18,Fto how damaging gang culture has
OL,19,Fbecome for young people.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1783700376
OL,3,CEnfield drill rappers found guilty of
OL,4,Cmurder provoked by social media fight
OL,6,F"Too many children are losing their
OL,7,Flives and too many families are being
OL,8,Fleft to suffer unimaginable heartbreak.
OL,10,F"Something must change before more
OL,11,Fyoung lives are taken and more parents
OL,12,Fare forced to endure the pain that we
OL,13,Fnow live with every day."
OL,15,FDetective Chief Inspector Lucie Card,
OL,16,Fwho led the investigation said:
OL,26,@rD@AOUuD@YO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1783700376
OL,3,CEnfield drill rappers found guilty of
OL,4,Cmurder provoked by social media fight
OL,6,F"Our painstaking investigation
OL,7,Festablished that Keanu was murdered
OL,8,Fbecause his killers took offence to
OL,9,Fsomething that was said in a social
OL,10,Fmedia group chat.
OL,12,F"Rather than ignore the comments,
OL,13,FEmmanuel Popoola armed himself with a
OL,14,Fpistol and with the help of Teyvon
OL,15,FEtefia carried out a drive-by shooting.
OL,17,F"This was cowardly and
OL,18,Fdisproportionate violence that has
OL,19,Funderstandably shocked the community."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU{D@fO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/10
