OL,3,CEnfield drill rappers found guilty of
OL,4,Cmurder provoked by social media fight
OL,6,FEtefia and Popoola will be sentenced
OL,7,Fat the Old Bailey on Thursday and
OL,8,FFriday.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/10
